# GRAPHICS::GET_SCREENBLUR_FADE_CURRENT_TIME

## Returns
* **FLOAT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns the current time (in milliseconds of the fade effect).
Returns 0 if no fade was active
